\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/27\/created-for-tawbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":22676,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Repentance: Allah created people to forgive them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"If you were not to sin, Allah would surely create people who would sin and He would forgive them.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2748 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064e\u064a\u064f\u0651\u0648\u0628\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32689,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/06\/abu-darda-act-upon-knowledge\/","url_meta":{"origin":22676,"position":5},"title":"Abu Darda on Judgment: Did you not act upon your knowledge?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Luqman reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, I fear from my Lord on the Day of Resurrection that I will be called in front of the heads of all creation, saying: O \u2018Uwaymir! I will say: At your service, my Lord. He will say: Did\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":